1165
00:44:06,110 --> 00:44:07,690
I wonder if I can help you.

1166
00:44:07,970 --> 00:44:08,580
You know how to do this too?

1167
00:44:08,300 --> 00:44:11,140
♫Getting closer gently♫

1168
